name: Motorbike EX | Transportation LoRA
description:
Here's a LoRA that produces cool motorbike images.

MAJOR UPDATE

The robustness of the new version v0.9 is very high, enjoy it.

USE: Width 512 or Height 512

Key Prompt

View

  • front view

  • side view

  • back view, looking back

Position

  • sitting

  • driving

  • leaning...posing for a picture

Pose (poor effect)

  • legs outstretched, feet on the ground, posing for a picture

  • feet on stand

Clothing

  • in a racing outfit

  • in a motorbike helmet

ALSO Works with my other two LoRAs

  • UrbanSamurai_fashion (note, it can only be used with the fashion version, not with the v0.3 version)

  • Cyberhelmet

Adaptation

  • Real 3D --> Good

  • 2.5D --> Good (v0.2)

  • 2D --> GOOD (v0.9)

歡迎朋友們加我微信交流：artist3yehe

Reach me on Twitter if you wish to contribute to improving this mod, Thx!

https://twitter.com/Artist3YeHe
